IntakeFormSectionPtcp.name: IntakeFormSectionPtcp
IntakeFormSectionPtcp.description: Represents information about a user or group of participants who have access to an intake form section.

Comments.description: The comments about why the participant has access to the intake form section.

IntakeFormSectionId.description: The intake form section associated with the intake form section participant record.

IsActive.description: Specifies whether the participant's association with the intake form section is active (true) or not (false).

LastReferencedDate.description: The timestamp for when the current user last viewed a record related to this record.

Name.description: The name of the intake form section participant.

ParticipantId.description: The participant associated with the intake form section participant record.

ParticipantRoleId.description: The participant role associated with the intake form section participant record.
